cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.AR, cs.NE 

This paper focuses on designing efficient convolutional neural networks for different types of hardware, which is a common problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also proposes a novel algorithm for Neural Architecture Search (NAS), which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and robotics (cs.AR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of hardware accelerators such as DSP and VPU, which are relevant to computer engineering (cs.NE).
